properties.name: NONE
properties.description: Does not use a fitting option.

properties.name: CONTENT_TO_FRAME
properties.description: Resizes content to fit the frame. Note: Content that has different proportions than the frame appears stretched or squeezed.

properties.name: PROPORTIONALLY
properties.description: Resizes content to fit the frame while preserving content proportions. If the content and frame have different proportions, some empty space appears in the frame.

properties.name: FILL_PROPORTIONALLY
properties.description: Resizes content to fill the frame while perserving the content's proportions. If the content and frame have different proportions, some of the content is obscured by the frame.

name: EmptyFrameFittingOptions
description: Options for fitting content in an empty frame.
